data.name: metroLabel7.Text
data.value: Made with <3 for those having problems modding and playing Blade and Soul Features: - Unattended: Run Game Unsupervised(Bypass Startup Dialogs). - No Texture Streaming: Force Loading of textures locally(Improves Speed). - Fix Loading Screen: Remove Loading screen files to improve loading speed. - Splash Changer: Change the splash image when starting the game. - Mod Manager: Easier management of mods for your game. - Dat Editor: Edit BnS's Arbitrary data files to your liking. - Donators: Name of all the lovely people who donated for my coffee. - Addons: Dat Editing to a whole new level of automation. Credits: - Endless: Because I was part of the low-end boat. | ronny1982: BnSDat - Miyako: Whom I was inspired from | LokiReborn: Port BnSDat and Token
